        <h1>Getting Started with AeroGear</h1>
          
        <p>
          AeroGear consists of a backend service in OpenShift cloud platform, and client libraries for various mobile platforms.</p>

        <p>Follow the tutorials linked below to get everything set up, installed and build your first mobile application using AeroGear.</p>
        
  </div>
</div>

